This repository contains a fully interactive Excel Sales Performance Dashboard created using advanced Excel features such as Pivot Tables, Slicers, Charts, Conditional Formatting, and Dynamic Analysis. The dashboard visualizes key business metrics including:

Total Sales

Total Revenue

Total Orders

Return Rate

Product Category Performance

Region-wise Sales

Year-wise Sales Trend

Payment Method Distribution

Return Analysis

Delivery Day Averages

The dashboard is designed for business analytics, data visualization, and decision-making. It can serve as a strong portfolio project for data analyst roles, showcasing Excel skills, dashboard design, and KPI reporting.
